In medium bowl, combine cookie crumbs and butter. Using back of spoon, press 2 rounded tablespoons crumb mixture in bottom and up sides of 24 (2 1/2 -inch) paper-cup-lined muffin cups. In large bowl, combined EAGLE BRAND(r), creme de menthe, schnapps and food coloring (optional). Fold in whipped cream. Spoon mixture into prepared cups. Freeze 6 hours or until firm. To serve, remove paper liners. Garnish as desired. Store leftovers covered in freezer.